title: Fogless Shower Mirror with Squeegee by ToiletTree Products. Guaranteed to NEVER fog or your money back!
description: ToiletTree Products has perfected the fogless shower mirror industry. With patents to support the concept, we set ourselves apart from the rest of the "competition"Like all of our mirrors, this fogless shower mirror is guaranteed not to fog in the shower - EVER. Stop buying other fogless shower mirrors that just don't work. This mirror comes with specially designed suctions cups allowing you to detach it and take your mirror with your anywhere. The mirror is simple to use, just fill the reservoir before each use! An included self-stored squeegee removes any excess water from the front of your mirror. The mirror comes with an included drawstring pouch to protect your mirror while its not being used. Dermatologists recommend performing daily skin care regimen in the shower as this promotes healthier looking skin. The combination of heat and moisture open the pores and creates an ideal environment for shaving, exfoliating, tweezing and cleaning. Great for college dorms, traveling on vacation and business trips.To use: Simply fill the reservoir with hot shower water before each use. The hot water will keep the mirror the same temperature as the environment in your shower which makes it scientifically impossible for your mirror to ever fog.This mirror is 4.75 inches x 5.5 inches. It is small enough to fit directly in your toiletry travel bag, yet large enough to get the job done everyday. If you are looking for a larger, or a fogless mirror that doesn't use suction cups, check out our original version of this product.
